            Welcome!
          
          
            
          
          
            This is the website for Abby Flynt, PhD.
            I am a statistician and Associate Professor in the Department of Mathematics at Bucknell University in Lewisburg, Pennsylvania. Ray Bucknell!
            I received a Bachelor of Science degree in Mathematics Secondary Education from SUNY Fredonia and a Masters and PhD in Statistics from Carnegie Mellon University.
